## ğŸ“ Quick Reference

### Common Modifiers Order
```swift
.font()
.foregroundColor()
.padding()
.background()
.cornerRadius()
.shadow()
```

### Safe Navigation
```swift
NavigationLink(destination: DetailView(item: item)) {
    // Link content
}
```

### Conditional Rendering
```swift
if condition {
    View1()
} else {
    View2()
}
```

